---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Over ons | SASA" bodyClass="bg-background font-body text-on-surface antialiased">
<main>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-8 overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-6">
<span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-primary-container/10 text-primary font-bold tracking-wider text-xs uppercase rounded-full px-el" data-depth="0.9">Ons verhaal</span>
<h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-on-background leading-tight px-el" data-depth="0.5">
  Bouwen aan <span class="text-primary italic">duurzame</span> digitale landschappen.
</h1>
<p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed max-w-xl px-el" data-depth="0.3">
  Bij SASA overbruggen we de kloof tussen complexe technologie en intuïtieve menselijke ervaringen, geworteld in groei en helderheid.
</p>
</div>
<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative px-el" data-depth="0.4">
<div class="aspect-square rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden vibrant-glow">
<img alt="SASA team" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" src="/team-foto.jpg"/>
</div>
<div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-primary p-8 rounded-full shadow-xl">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-4xl">eco</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Mission & Vision -->
<section class="py-24 space-y-32">
<!-- Mission -->
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
<div class="order-2 md:order-1">
<div class="relative group">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary translate-x-4 translate-y-4 rounded-xl -z-10 opacity-20 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-6 group-hover:translate-y-6"></div>
<img alt="Samenwerkend team in vergadering" class="w-full h-[450px] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-2xl" src="https://placehold.co/800x450"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="order-1 md:order-2 space-y-6">
<div class="bg-primary-container p-12 rounded-xl layered-shadow">
<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold text-on-primary-container mb-4">Onze missie</h2>
<p class="text-lg text-on-primary-container/80 leading-relaxed">
  Vooruitstrevende merken versterken met krachtige digitale tools die zowel de gebruiker als de omgeving respecteren. Wij geloven in groei die ethiek en elegantie niet opoffert.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Vision -->
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="bg-secondary p-12 rounded-xl layered-shadow">
<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold text-on-secondary mb-4">Onze visie</h2>
<p class="text-lg text-on-secondary/80 leading-relaxed">
  Een wereld waarin digitale ervaringen zo natuurlijk en essentieel aanvoelen als de lucht die we inademen. Wij stellen de wereldwijde standaard voor ethisch design en engineering.
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="relative group">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#7bd345] -translate-x-4 translate-y-4 rounded-xl -z-10 opacity-20 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-6 group-hover:translate-y-6"></div>
<img alt="Abstracte digitale verbindingen" class="w-full h-[450px] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-2xl" src="https://placehold.co/800x450"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Core Ethos Section -->
<section class="py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 text-center mb-20">
<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#1A2E26] mb-4">Onze kernwaarden</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg">De principes die elke beslissing die we nemen sturen.</p>
</div>
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-start">
<!-- Value 1 -->
<div class="value-card group flex flex-col px-el w-full sm:w-[calc(50%-1rem)] lg:w-[calc(20%-1.6rem)]" data-depth="0.6">
  <div class="w-8 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#9fe870] mb-5 group-hover:w-12 transition-all duration-300"></div>
  <h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold mb-3 text-[#1A2E26]">Radicale intentie</h3>
  <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Elk pixel en elke regel code wordt geplaatst met doelbewuste opzet om de reis van de gebruiker te verbeteren.</p>
</div>
<!-- Value 2 -->
<div class="value-card group flex flex-col px-el w-full sm:w-[calc(50%-1rem)] lg:w-[calc(20%-1.6rem)] kw-offset-2" data-depth="0.8">
  <div class="w-8 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#9fe870] mb-5 group-hover:w-12 transition-all duration-300"></div>
  <h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold mb-3 text-[#1A2E26]">Organische schaalbaarheid</h3>
  <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Architecturen ontworpen om te groeien. Flexibele systemen waarmee merken kunnen uitbreiden zonder wrijving.</p>
</div>
<!-- Value 3 -->
<div class="value-card group flex flex-col px-el w-full sm:w-[calc(50%-1rem)] lg:w-[calc(20%-1.6rem)] kw-offset-3" data-depth="0.5">
  <div class="w-8 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#9fe870] mb-5 group-hover:w-12 transition-all duration-300"></div>
  <h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold mb-3 text-[#1A2E26]">Esthetische integriteit</h3>
  <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Schoonheid is een vereiste voor vertrouwen. Wij handhaven hoge visuele standaarden op alle platforms.</p>
</div>
<!-- Value 4 -->
<div class="value-card group flex flex-col px-el w-full sm:w-[calc(50%-1rem)] lg:w-[calc(20%-1.6rem)] kw-offset-4" data-depth="0.7">
  <div class="w-8 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#9fe870] mb-5 group-hover:w-12 transition-all duration-300"></div>
  <h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold mb-3 text-[#1A2E26]">Duurzame innovatie</h3>
  <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Langetermijnwaarde boven kortetermijntrends. Innovaties gebouwd op solide, duurzame fundamenten.</p>
</div>
<!-- Value 5 -->
<div class="value-card group flex flex-col px-el w-full sm:w-[calc(50%-1rem)] lg:w-[calc(20%-1.6rem)] kw-offset-5" data-depth="0.9">
  <div class="w-8 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#9fe870] mb-5 group-hover:w-12 transition-all duration-300"></div>
  <h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold mb-3 text-[#1A2E26]">Mensgerichte tech</h3>
  <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Tech moet mensen dienen. Wij ontwerpen eerst voor de menselijke ervaring, waarbij we empathie waarborgen.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Tijdlijn Section -->
<section class="py-24 px-8 bg-surface-container-low">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
<div class="space-y-12">
<div class="space-y-4">
<h2 class="font-headline text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#1A2E26] px-el" data-depth="0.5">Onze <span class="text-primary">Tijdlijn</span></h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg">Van eerste idee tot groeiend succes — ons verhaal in vier fases.</p>
</div>
<div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl px-el" data-depth="0.8">
<img alt="SASA team" class="w-full h-72 object-cover" src="/team-foto.jpg"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative pl-12 space-y-16">
<div class="absolute left-0 top-4 bottom-4 w-0.5 bg-verdant-accent/30"></div>
<!-- Phase 01 -->
<div class="relative px-el" data-depth="0.3">
<div class="absolute -left-[54px] top-1.5 w-4 h-4 bg-white border-2 border-primary rounded-full z-10 flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_0_8px_rgba(123,211,69,0.1)]">
<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase">Fase 01</span>
<h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-background">Startup</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Begonnen als twee studenten met een missie: elke startende ondernemer verdient een professionele online aanwezigheid. Vanuit een kleine kamer bouwden we onze eerste websites met passie en ambitie.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Phase 02 -->
<div class="relative px-el" data-depth="0.3">
<div class="absolute -left-[54px] top-1.5 w-4 h-4 bg-white border-2 border-primary rounded-full z-10 flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_0_8px_rgba(123,211,69,0.1)]">
<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase">Fase 02</span>
<h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-background">Eerste klanten</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Onze eerste klanten vertrouwden ons met hun online identiteit. Van mond-tot-mondreclame groeide ons klantenbestand organisch — elk project beter dan het vorige en elke samenwerking een leermoment.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Phase 03 -->
<div class="relative px-el" data-depth="0.3">
<div class="absolute -left-[54px] top-1.5 w-4 h-4 bg-white border-2 border-primary rounded-full z-10 flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_0_8px_rgba(123,211,69,0.1)]">
<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase">Fase 03</span>
<h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-background">100 klanten</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Een mijlpaal die bewees dat onze aanpak werkt. 100 tevreden ondernemers die hun doelen online bereiken, met een gemiddelde stijging van 40% in online zichtbaarheid en conversie.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Phase 04 -->
<div class="relative px-el" data-depth="0.3">
<div class="absolute -left-[54px] top-1.5 w-4 h-4 bg-white border-2 border-primary rounded-full z-10 flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_0_8px_rgba(123,211,69,0.1)]">
<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase">Fase 04</span>
<h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-background">Groei &amp; Succes</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Vandaag helpen we honderden Nederlandse ondernemers met razendsnel groeiende digitale aanwezigheid. We zijn er trots op te zeggen: we zijn nog maar net begonnen.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
